(3, 'I Meditate NY: Urban Meditation Series ', 'I Meditate NY: Urban Meditation Series ', '<p>I Meditate NY has created an Urban Meditation Series for BGL to be held every Saturday at 10am from August 6th until October 15th. This series introduces meditation to empower participants to contemplate what “comfort” means to them. It will provide a technique that examines the inner environment to enhance the outer environment. Sessions will aim to challenge comfort zones and provide a tool to create sustainable comfort: comfort that comes from within and goes with you. Each session will include an introduction to meditation.</p>', '2011-08-09 19:23:39', '2011-08-09 19:23:59', NULL, 'aug6_1.jpg', '', 0, '');
